arget=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"aea6f81a7df33a2ecc260266ce03b13dcd296463","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b91772196b0c6a9629b9771fa35bb583d3ccf5c","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:14:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0146c11480e93fcdb088c9c9de0d67c8662efbd","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"268503da965749cbc004409ac93c815f81b38da1","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fee28fe684d33c55f1b6b3d1044bfff2db3dd53","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97751f177182e67f40dcbae7189aba727427a5e8","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44e13b5c30d42056ab50772f2170af236e9b65c7","tid":1695844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec0d96018103ab41e059cd059a8428d6ac95c4c","tid":1695844,"uid":243437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"198b65e53ed0f91ee6418a36bda617